## Horizontal rule

---

A broken table degrades to a dash row, which must stay visible:

First Header | Second Header
------------ ------------
Content | Content

 ---

(heading H2 @0..19
  "Horizontal rule")
(paragraph @20..24
  "---")
(paragraph @25..89
  "A broken table degrades to a dash row, which must stay visible:")
(paragraph @90..119
  "First Header | Second Header")
(paragraph @119..145
  "------------ ------------")
(paragraph @145..163
  "Content | Content")
